name: Unicons Outline Remixed
description:
Unicons Icons remixed (Outline)


  • Corrected Icons (Clocks centre alignment, Volleyball icon added and vector corrected)
  • Re-organized into frames for a better assets panel experience and for scalability
  • Auto-layed out with auto-layout (simply rearrange your icons by drag and drop or using arrow keys)
  • Perfect for shared libraries


Enjoy
